# ApplyTracker Project Rules

## Project Vision
ApplyTracker is an intelligent job search manager that uses Together AI for discovery and semantic analysis.

## Technical Stack
- Backend: FastAPI (Uvicorn)
- Frontend: React (Tailwind CSS)
- AI: Together AI (Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-Turbo)

## Core Guidelines
- Use modular structure (separate service files for AI logic).
- Follow the Kanban stages: Discovery, Applied, Interviewing, Offer, Rejected.
- Always load API keys from a .env file.